{"tid":1697220,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"超突發! 食完藍絲/紅底野食肚痛肚屙到要SL! 老豆老母驚左話以後唔買! 肚痛師!?","createTime":"2019-11-06T16:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:38:31.000Z","uid":4322,"like":144,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f25c5c3d257bebf24c1f38897403d60eceaa3a0b","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"簡單介紹下 <br />\n老豆深藍 老母淺藍<br />\n咁老豆成日就鍾意食藍絲/紅底 加料都要大家樂/美心 唔藍唔食<br />\n咁我無計喇 唔通唔食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>唔食都無事 近日每次一食藍店就開始肚痛! </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n有次仲食完飯就去左廁所屙幾次!<br />\n第二日攪到我要SL! 幾撚嚴重! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好古怪! <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>食黃店就一定無事!</ins></strong></span> 有無手足知咩事?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家攪攪下老母都買多左黃店野食 連加料老豆都唔敢亂買了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母仲周圍同相熟師奶講我食完邊間肚屙到SL!<br />\n依家佢圍內師奶都唔食佢了!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我正式宣佈新職業 - 肚痛師正式面世! </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n好簡單 相信大家好熟黃藍店list<br />\n我地今次目標唔是連鎖餐廳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>我地今次要針死藍絲紅底小店!</ins></strong></span><br />\n原因係佢地無連鎖咁多錢 無咁易捱到<br />\n而且唔出名 老豆老母唔識分黃藍<br />\n唔會第一下覺得你係扮野<br />\n你試下扮食美心肚痛 佢地未必信<br />\n對付醒少少既藍<br />\n可以一開波話唔知係咪食錯野先<br />\n之後過一兩次先扮傻問佢地買邊間<br />\n最後出埋肚屙SL大招 (食埋瀉藥亦可!)<br />\n叫佢地不如買第間(黃店)喇 <br />\n唔肯就自己去買<br />\n成本係零 但效果隨時無限<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">都係個句 經師奶口中宣傳 好過你講一萬次</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e12fd9a1aea1a42edc50165cc1d5169fafd4256c","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"[米豬連] 十八區黃店自發組米豬連聯盟 可由出名黃店牽頭(渣哥/龍門/一芳/水門) 互相提供優惠/請手足工作!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697221</a>"},{"pid":"e0e43997f75cc0c9f8ae89aa83df18f726e18f33","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:51:31.000Z","msg":"pishhh"},{"pid":"d41436f8dd248686de3d3ca94a4e829ab4deeeca","tid":1697220,"uid":74163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"咁有創意。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cb0a9775746bcc1c796b0fe853afe501e728b9","tid":1697220,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db83821e52b3ff3cc61a62d6b5f667b545e628ff","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d41436f8dd248686de3d3ca94a4e829ab4deeeca","tid":1697220,"uid":74163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"咁有創意。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"本人咩都無 只有無窮創意同堅持"},{"pid":"e4601b8fd16a982844052802ee774cd83da3e083","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"pishhhh"},{"pid":"06afedf78d0ae7e4cd97fdee76afaeed66750f4f","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"pishhhhh"},{"pid":"641e2e0db2964296ad38beef0de2616ce96d3113","tid":1697220,"uid":263912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10d93b2c3dc224edf7170d344228dd07196932a","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"