<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n我出黎同時做幫大家上Buff<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人（我😎）<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家強身健體<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n由改變自己 再感染多一個人<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需 要TG 唔問名 <br />\n唔會問聯絡資料<br />\n同你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n如果想做下運動放鬆<br />\n歡迎黎搵我做下運動 <br />\n有街頭健身<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=be2b1902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=689e6b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=7f1cc277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n唔駛驚冇工開 <br />\n想開工/彈性part time<br />\n可以黎搵我 我cover你<br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"21727648234e686a943e7460f06780378fac0314","tid":1697220,"uid":123765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:23:38.000Z","msg":"新職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dde3dd6a2236177ff9303618a0c6a2d0a5e26fa","tid":1697220,"uid":112433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:25:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d4239d17229f41c6b5e25b115c92f64da35a84e","tid":1697220,"uid":316055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9814eaa62b529db2512334a9ce153b9fd57312","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeaea12c78bb2c8428a1ce7290c576bc4390d21d","tid":1697220,"uid":173191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"藍店1823食環報有老鼠衞生問題 <br />\n做埋肚痛師 會唔會加速收皮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔好報食環消防稅局呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d6b9ead2c4025bb58ee12a5970d9abfdbf20b276","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"19dc2db3fac751952c302aaecfad4e759105e978","tid":1697220,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46eb94564eb02d4e2c44c6a3ba6d07000dd38c2c","tid":1697220,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T22:35:04.000Z","msg":"must push<br />\n笑死 諗起要拎埋部電話入廁所幾次<br />\n打住機扮肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"rep